    "The framework used edge computing and blockchain technology for scalability and security, as well as privacy [7].",
    "demonstrated a privacy-preserving scheme for the finegrained access control of large-scale health data based on blockchain technology.",
    "The scheme was divided into five layers.",
    "Its security was ensured by using signing, symmetric, and asymmetric methods.",
    "It was evaluated for performance and security by comparing it to a conventional scheme that had basic security features [25].In another study, Liu et al."
